title: Illaoi E Bug with Wukong?
body: Is this supposed to be a thing? my e was negated by wukong e? P.S. will need vlc media player to open this file. Happened several times throughout the match.

replies.body: It's definitely possible that might be a bug. I'd drop a post in the [Report a Bug](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) sub-board on the North American Boards. Rioters check the Report a Bug sub-board pretty regularly, and reports help them track bugs and issues!
